mozambique ( or ) , officially the republic of mozambique ( or , ) , is a country in southeast africa bordered by the indian ocean to the east , tanzania to the north , malawi and zambia to the northwest , zimbabwe to the west , and swaziland and south africa to the southwest .

the 1980s : on march 16 , 1984 this country signed its first peace treaty with a black - ruled nation , mozambique

